$interpreted: Religious Soldier: If a slave murders a master, he must be slain immediately! A Priest has died, and you want to bring him into custody!
Nationalist Soldier: Queen Diana demands that we uphold the law. We must bring suspected criminals before a judge, and you know it!
Religious Soldier: The Queen's actions are just for show! The High Priest and the Holy Mother are the only ones concerned about the people!
Sanchez: (The soldiers are pissed and the judges are busy as hell. They'll probably give us the death sentence just to save time...I don't want to die!)
Sanchez: (Better make my escape while they're arguing!)
Rune: Sanchez...what are you doing?
Sanchez: Nincompoop! Stop following me!
Religious Soldier: Stand still! Where do you think you're going?
Rune: Argh!!
Rune: Uh...oh yeah...Sanchez said...don't cause...trouble...
Sanchez: ...Dying anywhere else is better than here...
Castle Guard: Hey! What are you two doing?
Maid: Since Queen Diana is shutting down the Martyrs' Colosseum, she has to deal with the nobles every day. She has no time to come here herself.
Head House-maid: It's a shame everyone thinks her actions are cowardly. The High Priest has enormous support in his effort to reopen the colosseum.
Diana: I won't let him succeed.
Head House-maid: The Queen, Your Majesty.
Diana: How are my babies doing?
Head House-maid: Just fine, Your Majesty. They'll hatch after a few days.
Maid: Since General Lazer has arrived, why don't we go together?
Lazer: The Queen is concerned with national matters. I'll just stay here and make sure everything is safe.
Maid: But...
Diana: If that is what the General wants, then let him be.
Maid: Wahhhhhh!!!!!
Sanchez: No! You ran the wrong way!!
Castle Guard: Stop right there!!
Lazer: What's the matter?
Castle Guard: General, these two slaves are suspected of attempting to murder the master, but they escaped while in custody!
Lazer: What!? The Queen is here. Get them immediately!
Castle Guard: Yes, sir!
Sanchez: Help me! Please!
Head House-maid: Don't touch those eggs!!
Sanchez: Don't come any closer! I'll smash it, I swear!
Rune: Smash...all.
Diana: No! That's the offspring of the Royal Lizard family and the Lizard nobles. Do you dare!?
Sanchez: At worst, we all die. What's there to be scared of?
Rune: ...scared...?
Rune: ...Alive...they're alive...they're...babies...
Sanchez: You useless piece of junk. I'll do it myself!
Rune: No!!!
Rune: Put down...the babies.
Sanchez: You nut! We're on the same side! Let go!
Castle Guard: Ergh!!
Diana: No!!
Maid: Ahhhh!! I can't watch!
Head House-maid: Whew~ Thank God nothing happened...
Diana: ...Let them go.
Diana: Lazer.
Lazer: Listen and listen closely. Bring back those two along with the eggs. You will not let the High Priest find out about this.
